Weinstein Creates Label for Film Distribution; First Release Expected 2012

-- B y   M i c h a e l   W h i t e
-- 
2011-09-06T21:44:25Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-06/weinstein-creates-label-for-film-distribution-first-release-expected-2012.html
Weinstein Co., the film studio led
by Harvey and Bob Weinstein, created a new label to
simultaneously offer movies in digital and traditional media.  The company formed the new unit with Tom Quinn and Jason
Janego, former executives of  Magnolia Pictures , according to a
statement today from New York-based Weinstein. They expect the
first release in the first half of 2012.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Michael White in  Los Angeles  at 
 mwhite8@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Rob Golum at 
 rgolum@bloomberg.net  